metadata.name: Cyberchrome
metadata.description:
#1 - Cyberchrome

Lurking in the endless rain forests of Cryptocon, the Cyberchrome feeds on Sylansium, the life fluid runs in the bodies of other Crypto creatures.

It uses its sharp teeth to rip its prey’s Sylansium vessels and drink its content, while leaving its prey’s remaining for other Cryptovores to feed on.
